A common error with using _RecyclerView_ is to set a value in the item view when some condition is met but not setting the value when the condition is not met. Remember that view holders are reused (recycled) by the _RecyclerView_.

Your problem code is the following:

     if (position &gt; 0)
            {
                if (messages.get(position - 1).isSent() != sent)
                {
                    RecyclerView.LayoutParams layoutParams = (RecyclerView.LayoutParams) holder.messagesReceivedLayout.getRoot().getRootView().getLayoutParams();
                    layoutParams.topMargin = 80;
                    holder.messagesReceivedLayout.getRoot().getRootView().setLayoutParams(layoutParams);
                }
            }

You will always need to address the margin each time since you can&#39;t assume that it has the original value as defined in the layout file.

